source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: yaml/prettier-ignore/trailing-comma.yml
---

# Input

```yml
[
  # prettier-ignore
             {  sss  },       # 123
    {  qqqq },
  
  # prettier-ignore
          [ccc    ]       # 777
  , [ddd    ]
]

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,9 +1,8 @@
 [
   # prettier-ignore
   {  sss  }, # 123
-  { qqqq },
-
+  { ? qqqq },
   # prettier-ignore
   [ccc    ], # 777
-  [ddd],
+  [ddd]
 ]
```

# Output

```yml
[
  # prettier-ignore
  {  sss  }, # 123
  { ? qqqq },
  # prettier-ignore
  [ccc    ], # 777
  [ddd]
]
```
